name: ODIN
description:
The ancient Powers are awakening! It's time to remember who we really are!

ODIN is the most ancient deity. The forefather of all gods and men. 

The picture balances the Dark and Light sides of personality, gives powerful protection, and attunes to the Higher Meaning of Spirit.

Symbols in the painting:

Valcnut is the portal entrance to all 9 worlds of the universe.  Gives multidimensional perception.
⠀
Agiskhjalm - promotes protection from external influences, and the accumulation of personal Power.
⠀
Runic ligature - "Who Am I?" for finding your True Path and realizing your potential.
⠀
Circumstance - Symbol of the Most High.  The beginning of all beginnings.
⠀
Odin's Spear - the strongest weapon in the universe.

Antahkarana - the connection between the physical brain and the Higher Ego.
